column13: 2. Participants starting time varies, but mostly after Jan-10

3. Consumptioncounter starting from 0, and may jump more than 1 between observations. Each observation corresponds to a data collection point. Sometime it is about a new consumption, sometimes it is due to variation of sensor battery, ambient temperature or others. Consumption counter starts from 0.
4. Buttoncounter increments when participants press on the sensor
5. Data is sorted by each participant, then by event timestamp
